<p>Screaming Frog finds the problems. It does not fix them.</p>
<p>You ran a crawl. You exported a spreadsheet of 4,000 broken links, missing titles, and duplicate content. Now the spreadsheet sits in a folder no one opens. SEO issues compound like debt. The longer they wait, the more traffic you lose.</p>
<p>This guide reviews 7 genuine Screaming Frog alternatives — ranked by speed, price, and deployment type. At the end, you will find a decision matrix matched to team size and budget. You will also see where thestacc fits: not as a Screaming Frog replacement, but as the execution layer that publishes content after the audit finishes.</p>
