<p><strong>Is Screaming Frog worth $259 per year?</strong></p>
<p>Screaming Frog is worth the price for technical SEOs who need deep crawl control, custom extraction, and log file analysis. It is not worth the price for teams that need content production, collaboration, or cloud deployment. Those teams should pair Screaming Frog with a cloud tool or switch entirely.</p>
