<p>Sitebulb, Semrush, Ahrefs, Lumar, SE Ranking, JetOctopus, and thestacc are all cloud-based. Screaming Frog is the only major crawler that remains desktop-only.</p>
<p><strong>Does Screaming Frog write or publish content?</strong></p>
<p>No. Screaming Frog crawls websites and exports technical data. It does not write articles, publish pages, or distribute posts. For content production, you need a separate tool such as thestacc.</p>
<p><strong>What is an SEO crawler?</strong></p>
